				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">No, there is no such option.
<br />

<br />
However, you can edit the source code. In the file &quot;functions_tc.php&quot;, find
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$emailer-&gt;email_address&#40;$board_config&#91;'board_email'&#93;&#41;;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
and change to
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$emailer-&gt;email_address&#40;'email_address_you_want'&#41;;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
